{"tid":6711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本主題公園冰埋5000魚蝦蟹作溜冰體驗!!!!!","createTime":"2016-11-27T13:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T10:13:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77625cee76fb25930a47be9e015e1df2d063a874","tid":6711,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:30:12.000Z","msg":"很多主題公園假娛樂之名去勞役犧牲生命，當中位於日本福岡的遊樂場「太空世界」更殘忍恐怖，在本月12日於溜冰場推出「冰的水族館」主題，將多達5000條魚類、貝類、蝦蟹等屍體冰封在冰面下，還在其FACEBOOK推出宣傳照片，引來日本網民狂轟殘忍。太空世界其後公開道歉，並宣布取消有關主題。 <br />\n<br />\n該主題公園聲稱想讓遊客體驗在海洋世界溜冰的感覺，所以買下了5000條海洋生物，埋在冰下，有些魚屍更只得一半嵌在冰下，嘴巴張開，露出痛苦的神情。 <br />\n<br />\n有關做法引來網民狠批，太空世界隨即於專頁刪去該帖，指因為主題公園不適當的表現引來不快，所以刪去該帖及道歉。太空世界的網站亦發出聲明，指非常重視所收到的意見，為引起大家不快表達歉意，並會即日起停止有關主題，溜冰場會稍後才再開放。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php39EbpV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php39EbpV.jpg&h=9dc05f4d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n「冰之水族館」在冰面下埋了5000具魚類、貝類蝦蟹的屍體，引發日本民眾強烈抨擊，主辦單位今宣布活動中止。（圖擷取自臉書） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2016/new/nov/27/images/bigPic/400_400/phpzTpZXW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2016%2Fnew%2Fnov%2F27%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2FphpzTpZXW.jpg&h=f5df16ad&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n溜冰場的冰層底下埋著超過5000多隻各類性海洋生物屍體，企圖營造成在冰下游泳的噱頭，而這些魚類都是事先被凍成冰磚，載運到場內進行拼接。（圖擷取自臉書）"},{"pid":"2a930c717dcdadfaa1ddbe77cb7dd0256bf43e5f","tid":6711,"uid":5009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:30:47.000Z","msg":"支那咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3a5d0eb418ab280dc9593049b26ca81717e114","tid":6711,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:35:08.000Z","msg":"死既有乜好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6836b1931fd0d212a962b56b02481fcfa8ebf3","tid":6711,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"魚魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34272c6e7ccbd9af175b66bde243576c95a2be6c","tid":6711,"uid":12343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"概念幾得意既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但可以搵仿製品代替活生生既生物囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951709580c229ed702e87c623ae6ce606691deb2","tid":6711,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:45:52.000Z","msg":"點解你開咁多時事post 但張張都死圖黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4c4a979f8772d3dee4ec26bf1fb8b563996e8c","tid":6711,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:47:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解你開咁多時事post 但張張都死圖黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔清楚"},{"pid":"866ea347cb916940ee222beea3a731631c7578fb","tid":6711,"uid":349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>概念幾得意既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但可以搵仿製品代替活生生既生物囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仿製仲好啦又冇味"},{"pid":"38fc10d084125c83cb5530d0c5308b42f0e8f3d2","tid":6711,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"係支那應該會好受歡迎"},{"pid":"d64fbc4826248729fd564e3337ff7158d5805e2d","tid":6711,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"死魚魚😭😭"},{"pid":"08ab332f563ce93cd618bad43e582ad11d625284","tid":6711,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>很多主題公園假娛樂之名去勞役犧牲生命，當中位於日本福岡的遊樂場「太空世界」更殘忍恐怖，在本月12日於溜冰場推出「冰的水族館」主題，將多達5000條魚類、貝類、蝦蟹等屍體冰封在冰面下，還在其FACEBOOK推出宣傳照片，引來日本網民狂轟殘忍。太空世界其後公開道歉，並宣布取消有關主題。 <br />\n<